            "answer_text": "3^2 + (a-1)^2 = (a)^2\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026.(1) or. 9 + a^2 - 2a + 1 = a^2. or. 2.a = 10. or. a = 10/2 = 5. Putting a = 5 in eqn. (1) 3^2 + 4^2 = 5^2. (True , Pythagorean triplet ). Answer. ",
